nars.util.utf8

Class ByteBuf

  • java.lang.Object
    • nars.util.utf8.ByteBuf

  • public final class ByteBuf
extends java.lang.Object
    Byte Array Buffer Manipulation Tools, Adapted from Boon Methods: "add": adds content to the end, but will not grow the internal array. FAST "append": adds content to the end, growing as necessary "write": like append but can do some interpretation of the input value
